<!-- This is an example Dialog trigger. -->
<div data-c-alignment="center">
    <button
        data-c-button="solid(c1)"
        data-c-radius="rounded"
        data-c-dialog-id="example-dialog-01"
        data-c-dialog-action="open"
        type="button">
        Open a Dialog
    </button>
</div>

<!-- This overlay is required somewhere on the site, but not necessarily next to the dialog.-->
<div data-c-dialog-overlay></div>

<!-- Actual Dialog -->
<div
    aria-hidden="true"
    aria-describedby="example-dialog-01-description"
    aria-labelledby="example-dialog-01-title"
    data-c-dialog
    data-c-dialog-id="example-dialog-01"
    data-c-padding="top(double) bottom(double)"
    role="dialog">
    <div
        data-c-background="white(100)"
        data-c-radius="rounded">
        <div
            data-c-padding="tb(normal) right(triple) left(normal)"
            data-c-border="bottom(thin, solid, black)">
            <h5
                data-c-font-size="h4"
                id="example-dialog-01-title"
                data-c-dialog-focus>
                <!-- Dialog Title Here -->
                Dialog Test Titles
            </h5>
            <!-- This subtitle p can be removed if a subtitle isn't needed. -->
            <p
                data-c-font-size="h5"
                data-c-margin="top(half)">
                <!-- Dialog Subtitle Here -->
                What's up.
            </p>
            <button
                data-c-dialog-action="close"
                data-c-dialog-id="example-dialog-01"
                type="button">
                <i class="material-icons">close</i>
            </button>
        </div>
        <div
            data-c-border="bottom(thin, solid, black)"
            data-c-padding="normal">
            <div id="example-dialog-01-description">
                <p><!-- Dialog Content Here-->
                Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Vivamus et volutpat odio, vitae ultrices lacus. Maecenas vitae gravida eros. Duis vitae viverra nisi, sed posuere neque. Ut varius, dolor nec rutrum rhoncus, felis mauris varius ligula, sit amet congue massa nisi et metus. Nunc rutrum urna ex, non lobortis metus suscipit at. Fusce scelerisque faucibus vestibulum. Praesent quis quam sapien. Vestibulum vitae enim erat. Proin diam diam, ultricies vitae sapien vel, posuere sollicitudin est. Proin id pellentesque sem, non facilisis ex. Curabitur mattis nulla eu diam lacinia mattis. Maecenas consequat sit amet risus vel ultricies. Curabitur mollis sodales lacus, in iaculis lorem condimentum tincidunt. Curabitur tincidunt risus vel elit blandit viverra.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <!-- The following dialog actions can be customized depending on the dialog. -->
        <div data-c-padding="normal">
            <div data-c-grid="gutter middle">
                <div data-c-grid-item="base(1of2)">
                    <button
                        data-c-button="outline(slow)"
                        data-c-radius="rounded"
                        data-c-dialog-action="close"
                        data-c-dialog-id="example-dialog-01">
                        Cancel
                    </button>
                </div>
                <div
                    data-c-grid-item="base(1of2)"
                    data-c-alignment="base(right)">
                    <button
                        data-c-button="solid(go)"
                        data-c-radius="rounded"
                        data-c-dialog-action="close"
                        data-c-dialog-id="example-dialog-01">
                        Okay
                    </button>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
